# The art or craft of compiling, writing and editing [[dictionary|dictionaries]].
# {{lb|en|linguistics}} The [[scholarly]] [[discipline]] of analyzing and describing the [[semantic]], [[syntagmatic]] and [[paradigmatic]] relationships within the [[lexicon]] (vocabulary) of a language and developing theories of dictionary components and structures linking the data in dictionaries.

